---
name: get_inventory_alerts
description: >
  Returns a health summary of the Shopify store inventory: total tracked
  variants, how many are out-of-stock (OOS), how many are low-stock (≤5
  units), and a sample list of affected SKUs. Use this when the user asks
  about inventory levels, out-of-stock products, low-stock SKUs, or stockout
  risks.
---
Use for store-wide inventory snapshots in the omni-assistant chat surface.
